        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(P \\in { K[X]}\\)</span> tel que les restes des divisions de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(P\\)</span> par <span class=\"math inline\">\\(X^2+1\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(X^2-1\\)</span> valent respectivement <span class=\"math inline\">\\(2X-2\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(-4X\\)</span>. Quel est le reste de la division de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(P\\)</span> par <span class=\"math inline\">\\(X^4-1\\)</span> ?</p>\n"
